#### New Features in v2.1.0 GUI

- **Version Display** - Shows v2.1.0 in title
- **Timestamps** - All messages show time [HH:MM]
- **Status Bar** - Shows current activity (Ready, Listening, Processing)
- **Help Button** - Quick access to commands
- **Better Colors** - User messages in green, assistant in blue, system in yellow
- **Hover Effects** - Buttons change color on hover
- **Thread Safety** - No more freezing during API calls

#### Button Functions

- **ðŸŽ¤ Voice** - Activate microphone for voice input (shows "â¸ï¸ Listening..." when active)
- **ðŸ“¤ Send** - Submit your typed message (or press Enter)
- **ðŸ—‘ï¸ Clear** - Clear conversation history with confirmation
- **â“ Help** - Show available commands (NEW in v2.1)
- **ðŸšª Exit** - Close the application with confirmation

#### Keyboard Shortcuts

- `Enter` - Send message
- `Shift + Enter` - New line in message
- `Ctrl + L` - Clear screen
- `Ctrl + Q` or `Ctrl + W` - Exit

