### 2. Status Bar (GUI Only)

Bottom of window shows:
- **"Ready"** - Waiting for input
- **"Listening..."** - Recording voice
- **"Recognizing..."** - Processing speech
- **"Processing..."** - Handling command
- **"Error"** - If something fails

### 3. Timestamps

All messages now have timestamps:
```
